# serviceagenda

Service Agenda is a simple API allowing users to magage their agendas.


# Group User

Resources related to a user in the API.

## User-Key [/v1/user/getkey{?username,password}]


+ Parameters
    - username : `root` (string, required) - User Name
    - password : `pass` (required)

### Get User Key [GET]

get a security key for operations later

+ Response 200 (application/json) 

    
        {
            "key":"h12bhj53"
            "permissions":["user","admin"]
        }


# Group Users

Resources related to users in the API.

### List all Users [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id":1
                "username":"freakkid"
                "password":"kidissad"
                "email":"freakkid@mail.sysu.edu.cn"
            },{
                "id":2
                "username":"freakkid1"
                "password":"kidissad1"
