            }
        ]

### Create a New User [POST]

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    
    + Headers
    
            Locations: /users/1
        
    + Body
    
            {
                "id":1
                "username":"freakkid"
                "password":"kidissad"
                "email":"freakkid@mail.sysu.edu.cn"
            }

### Get User by ID [GET /v1/users/{id}]

+ Parameters
    - id : `1` (int, required) - User Name
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id":1
            "username":"freakkid"
            "password":"kidissad"
            "email":"freakkid@mail.sysu.edu.cn"
        }